                        </button>
                      </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseSeventeen" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="Seventeen" data-parent="#accordion">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        There are some information about the authors in the Imprint which you find at the footer.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="card" style="margin-top: 5px;">
